Backend Development.
  1.Generate package.json file(contains complete information of our project)
    npm init -y
  2.Create HTTP server.
    -Install express module.
    npm install express or npm i express
    -Import express module

    -install monitor to restart server for every change
    npm install -g nodemon

  3.create API.
    REST API: REspresentational State Transfer, special api.
    structure of route: app.METHOD(path,request handler)
          medhod:get,post,put,update
          path:'/<url>'
          request handler{
            (request,response)=>{//callback fucntion,
            response.json("any javascript message to confirm working status")
            }
          }
    //api handle's the request